data.description: Fantastic 4 bed/3 bath home with pool and RV Parking in the heart of Silverado Ranch!  This gem features a covered patio, fully powered Tuff Shed and water softener throughout.  Located on a corner lot, the RV Parking extends to the rear yard and has a connected driveway.  Entry to the backyard from the kitchen or family room, so you can jump into the sparkling pool. Brand new water heater professionally installed!
